; Regression test for issue #515: --group-by account incompatible with --daily
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/515
; When combining --group-by account with --daily, each account group should only
; show its own postings. Previously, later groups incorrectly included all
; postings from preceding groups as well.

2017/06/01 income
    A   $30
    I

2017/06/01 buy
    Ex   $15
    A

2017/06/02 sell
    A   $10
    I

2017/06/03 buy
    Ex   $3
    A

test --group-by account --daily reg
A
17-Jun-01 - 17-Jun-01           A                               $15          $15
17-Jun-02 - 17-Jun-02           A                               $10          $25
17-Jun-03 - 17-Jun-03           A                               $-3          $22

Ex
17-Jun-01 - 17-Jun-01           Ex                              $15          $15
17-Jun-03 - 17-Jun-03           Ex                               $3          $18

I
17-Jun-01 - 17-Jun-01           I                              $-30         $-30
17-Jun-02 - 17-Jun-02           I                              $-10         $-40
end test
